body_html:
Hi lmatt-bit, that quantize_graph error is still not the latest tools described in https://www.tensorflow.org/performance/quantization

Did you try using the contrib/quantize library https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/quantize and then converting to TensorFlow Lite?

We will track support for t2t as well for the new tools. Thanks!
